        "en": "\"This is our homeroom,\" he said, standing in front of the half-opened door. \"We have Ms. Petosa. They say she's okay, at least for homeroom. I heard she's really strict if you get her for math, though.\" \"That's not true,\" said Charlotte. \"My sister had her last year and said she's totally nice.\" \"Not what I heard,\" answered Julian, \"but whatever.\" He closed the door and continued walking down the hallway.",
