        "en": "\"What's the deal with your face? I mean, were you in a fire or something?\" \"Julian, that's so rude!\" said Charlotte. \"I'm not being rude,\" said Julian, \"I'm just asking a question. Mr. Tushman said we could ask questions if we wanted to.\" \"Not rude questions like that,\" said Charlotte. \"Besides, he was born like that. That's what Mr. Tushman said. You just weren't listening.\" \"I was so listening!\" said Julian. \"I just thought maybe he was in a fire, too.\" \"Geez, Julian,\" said Jack. \"Just shut up.\" \"You shut up!\" Julian yelled.",
