        "en": "\"I don't know,\" answered the mummy. \"Tushman asked me to hang out with him at the beginning of the year, and he must have told all the teachers to put us next to each other in all our classes, or something.\" The mummy shrugged. I knew the shrug, of course. I knew the voice. I knew I wanted to run out of the class right then and there. But I stood where I was and listened to Jack Will finish what he was saying. \"I mean, the thing is: he always follows me around. What am I supposed to do?\" \"Just ditch him,\" said Julian.",
