        "en": "Mom knocked on my door after dinner. She looked drained, and I realized that between me and Auggie, today had been a tough day for her, too. \"So you want to tell me what's up?\" she asked nicely, softly. \"Not now, okay?\" I answered. I was reading. I was tired. Maybe later I'd be up to telling her about Miranda, but not now. \"I'll check in before you go to bed,\" she said, and then she came over and kissed me on the top of my head. \"Can Daisy sleep with me tonight?\" \"Sure, I'll bring her in later.\" \"Don't forget to come back,\" I said as she left. \"I promise.\"",
        "cn": "晚饭后妈妈敲了我的门。她看起来筋疲力尽，我意识到在我和奥吉之间，今天对她来说也是艰难的一天。“那么你想告诉我出什么事了吗？” 她和善地、轻柔地问。“现在不行，好吗？” 我回答。我正在看书。我累了。也许晚点我会有心情告诉她关于米兰达的事，但不是现在。“你睡觉前我再来看看你，” 她说，然后她走过来亲吻我的头顶。“今晚黛西能和我一起睡吗？” “当然，我晚点把它带进来。” “别忘了回来，” 她离开时我说。“我保证。”",
