        "id": 1,
        "en": "I was really excited because I got an invitation to Savanna's Halloween party. Savanna is probably the most popular girl in the school. All the boys like her. All the girls want to be friends with her. She was the first girl in the grade to actually have a \"boyfriend.\" It was some kid who goes to MS 281, though she dumped him and started dating Henry Joplin, which makes sense because the two of them totally look like teenagers already.",
        "cn": "我真的很兴奋，因为我收到了萨凡纳万圣节派对的邀请。萨凡纳可能是学校里最受欢迎的女孩。所有的男孩都喜欢她。所有的女孩都想和她做朋友。她是年级里第一个真正有“男朋友”的女孩。是某个上281中学的小子，不过她把他甩了，开始和亨利·乔普林约会，这很合理，因为他们俩看起来已经完全像青少年了。",
