        "en": "\"Jack, this is very, very serious,\" Mr. Tushman was saying. I was in his office, sitting on a chair across from his desk and looking at this picture of a pumpkin on the wall behind him. \"Kids get expelled for this kind of thing, Jack! I know you're a good kid and I don't want that to happen, but you have to explain yourself.\" \"This is so not like you, Jack,\" said Mom. She had come from work as soon as they had called her. I could tell she was going back and forth between being really mad and really surprised.",
