        "en": "Unfortunately, Mrs. G, who was the lunch teacher that day, saw what happened and chased after them. \"That's not allowed, boys!\" she scolded them loudly. \"This is not that kind of school. You get right back to your table.\" Oh great, like that was going to help. Before they could be forced to sit back down at the table, I got up with my tray and walked away really fast. I could hear Mrs. G call my name, but I pretended not to hear and just kept walking to the other side of the cafeteria, behind the lunch counter.",
