        "id": 4,
        "en": "\"Look, there's Justin,\" I said to Dad, pointing out Justin's picture in the program. \"That's a nice picture of him,\" he answered, nodding. \"How come there's no picture of Via?\" I said. \"She's an understudy,\" said Mom. \"But, look: here's her name.\" \"Why do they call her an understudy?\" I asked. \"Wow, look at Miranda's picture,\" said Mom to Dad. \"I don't think I would have recognized her.\" \"Why do they call it understudy?\" I repeated.",
