        "en": "The play was so amazing. I don't want to give away the ending, but it's the kind of ending that makes people in the audience teary. Mom totally lost it when Via-as-Emily said: \"Good-by, Good-by world! Good-by, Grover's Corners . . . Mama and Papa. Good-by to clocks ticking and Mama's sunflowers. And food and coffee. And new-ironed dresses and hot baths . . . and sleeping and waking up. Oh, earth, you're too wonderful for anybody to realize you!\"",
        "cn": "那场戏太棒了。我不想剧透结局，但那是那种能让观众潸然泪下的结局。当扮演艾米丽的维娅说出那段台词时，妈妈完全绷不住了：“再见，再见世界！再见，格罗弗角……爸爸妈妈。再见了，滴答作响的时钟和妈妈的向日葵。还有食物和咖啡。还有新熨的裙子和热水澡……还有睡觉和醒来。哦，地球，你太美好了，以至于没人能真正认识你！”",
