        "en": "I hardly saw Via at school this year, and when I did it was awkward. It felt like she was judging me. I knew she didn't like my new look. I knew she didn't like my group of friends. I didn't much like hers. We never actually argued: we just drifted away. Ella and I badmouthed her to each other: She's such a prude, she's so this, she's so that. We knew we were being mean, but it was easier to ice her out if we pretended she had done something to us. The truth is she hadn't changed at all: we had. We'd become these other people, and she was still the person she'd always been. That annoyed me so much and I didn't know why.",
        "cn": "今年我在学校几乎没见到维娅，见到时也很尴尬。感觉她在评判我。我知道她不喜欢我的新造型。我知道她不喜欢我的那群朋友。我也不太喜欢她的朋友。我们从未真正吵过架：我们只是渐行渐远了。艾拉和我会互相说她的坏话：她真是个老古板，她这样，她那样。我们知道我们很刻薄，但如果我们假装她对我们做了什么，把她排挤出去会更容易些。事实是她一点也没变：是我们变了。我们变成了另外的人，而她仍然是她一直以来的那个人。那让我非常恼火，我也不知道为什么。",
