        "id": 1,
        "en": "An announcement came over the huge speakers next to the stadium lights: \"Welcome, everyone. Welcome to the twenty-third annual Big Movie Night at the Broarwood Nature Reserve. Welcome, teachers and students from . . . MS 342: the William Heath School. . . .\" A big cheer went up on the left side of the field. \"Welcome, teachers and students from Glover Academy. . . .\" Another cheer went up, this time from the right side of the field. \"And welcome, teachers and students from . . . the Beecher Prep School!\" Our whole group cheered as loudly as we could.",
