        "id": 1,
        "en": "Mom was waiting for me in front of the school along with all the other parents when the bus arrived. Mr. Tushman told me on the bus ride home that they had called my parents to tell them there had been a \"situation\" the night before but that everyone was fine. He said the camp director and several of the counselors went looking for the hearing aid in the morning while we all went swimming in the lake, but they couldn't find it anywhere. Broarwood would reimburse us the cost of the hearing aids, he said. They felt bad about what happened.",
        "cn": "巴士到达时，妈妈和所有其他家长一样在学校门口等我。塔什曼先生在回家的巴士上告诉我，他们已经给你我的父母打了电话，告诉他们前一天晚上发生了“状况”，但所有人都没事。他说，早上我们都去湖里游泳时，营地主任和几位辅导员去找了助听器，但哪里也没找到。他说，布罗伍德会赔偿我们助听器的费用。他们对发生的事情感到很抱歉。",
