        "id": 1,
        "en": "About an hour later we were all seated in the giant auditorium waiting for Mr. Tushman to give his \"middleschool address.\" The auditorium was even bigger than I imagined it would be—bigger even than the one at Via's school. I looked around, and there must have been a million people in the audience. Okay, maybe not a million, but definitely a lot.",
